  ('aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-00531', 'aboriginal-f0899a01', 'aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-110-e2754278', 'sub-aboriginal-f0899a01-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '依刑法規定，下列何人脫逃，不成立脫逃罪？', '["依法管收之債務人", "依法逮捕之通緝犯", "依法監禁之受刑人", "依法傳喚之犯罪嫌疑人"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e6e107130816", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1c2f06e63016", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110150", "c": "507", "s": "0811", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "刑法概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "法警"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-00532', 'aboriginal-f0899a01', 'aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-110-e2754278', 'sub-aboriginal-f0899a01-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列罪名，何者並非屬於侵害國家司法權力作用之犯罪？', '["縱放人犯罪", "使公務員登載不實罪", "未指定犯人誣告罪", "頂替罪"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e6e107130816", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1c2f06e63016", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110150", "c": "507", "s": "0811", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "刑法概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "法警"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-00533', 'aboriginal-f0899a01', 'aboriginal-f0899a01-moex-110-e2754278', 'sub-aboriginal-f0899a01-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在公共場所聚集數人，意圖為強暴脅迫，已受該管公務員解散命令3次以上而不解散者，可能成立刑法第 149條妨害秩序罪。對於成立本罪應聚集之人數，下列敘述何者正確？', '["3人以上", "2人以上", "1人以上", "無人數之限制"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e6e107130816", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1c2f06e63016", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110150", "c": "507", "s": "0811", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "刑法概要", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "法警"}'::jsonb, NULL),
